Well, it's... It's mixed around 100 marine 
resources and around technical operating

18:33.477 --> 18:38.303
services. I do have copies downstairs on the third 
floor of each of these others. If you want to look at

18:44.931 --> 18:46.693
them, I think this is enough. All right. It's 
called Our Nation in the Sea. Yeah.

18:51.979 --> 18:54.382
Let's see if they get some more coffee. I don't 
know.

18:59.920 --> 19:01.723
And also that tribal language. You were making 
some comments about my dialect before, but that

